snippet.title: MXGP 2020 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Your new MXGP experience is coming... More real than ever!
Get ready to live the Official 2020 Championship and find the new amazing features! #MXGP2020 will be out on December 16th. Mud, Sweat and Glory.
